N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 154.8 - Refunds

State Regulations

The division shall refund any fee collected for which the
division did not comply with the time period for performance. Any fee for
expedited handling collected for any instrument which has been rejected by the
division shall be refunded if it is determined that the rejection was improper
or erroneous, and the requirements of these rules had been complied with by the
requestor of the services. Notes
